When I recklessly rush in to help
others...when all seems hopeless...he
is always there to protect me. Always.

Prince Michalis had admirable ideals
but is a man of little patience.
I cannot accept what he has done.

Nothing can go well if your heart is
not at peace. So please, get some
rest and calm your nerves.

Have you eaten yet? Even if you're in
a hurry, be sure to eat and stay
hydrated, $Nu.

I always cause so many problems for
Julian. If I were to go missing again,
he would surely worry.

Greetings. My name is Lena. I hope
your friendship will stay strong
with $Nf.

We must all extend compassion
to each other to prevent needless
loss of life.

Have courage so that we can walk
steadfast on a path that we believe in.
Please forgive my inexperience...

I thank you. May the gods'
blessing be upon you.

My name is Lena. If you are ever
feeling troubled, please allow me
to assist you.

Despite countless days of war in
another world, everyone in the Order
of Heroes stays so positive.$k$pTheir smiles cannot be taken for
granted, and their togetherness
serves to console others.$k$pI too have found myself in danger
before but have been saved by the
beaming faces of my loved ones.$k$pYour tireless dedication to supporting
the Order hasn't gone unseen...
However, who is supporting you?$k$pLet me extend warmth and a smile
whenever you need help. I think
Julian intends to do the same.

Stat away...!
きゃっ…
I will stop you!
Goddess, forgive me!
The goddess protects us!
That's quite enough!
Julian...
Giggle...
You're safe with me.
There is no cause for worry.
My name is Lena. I will assist you however I can.

However frightening my experiences have been,
my love for Julian has always seen me through.

I am a cleric. I cannot bear to watch others
come to harm when I have the power to help.
Julian... I am so sorry to have been a burden.
Whenever you are hurt, I will be there to heal you.
Guide me.
This might be difficult.
For the people.
